x.html#List.mapMonoM","doc":"Monomorphic `List.mapM`. The internal implementation uses pointer equality, and does not allocate a new list\nif the result of each `f a` is a pointer equal value `a`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.mapMonoM\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">mapMonoM</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1 → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Monad\">Monad</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">as</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/69a1d0485e241a494d69d3e2c98ad988f4396dcd/src/Init/Data/List/BasicAux.lean#L176-L181","name":"List.partitionMap.go","line":176,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.partitionMap.go","doc":"Auxiliary for `partitionMap`:\n`partitionMap.go f l acc₁ acc₂ = (acc₁.toList ++ left, acc₂.toList ++ right)`\nif `partitionMap f l = (left, right)`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.partitionMap.go\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">partitionMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">go</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">γ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_3}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">β</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Sum\">⊕</a> <span class=\"fn\">γ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <span class=\"fn\">γ</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">γ</span></span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/69a1d0485e241a494d69d3e2c98ad988f4396dcd/src/Init/Data/List/BasicAux.lean#L164-L181","name":"List.partitionMap","line":164,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.partitionMap","doc":"Given a function `f : α → β ⊕ γ`, `partitionMap f l` maps the list by `f`\nwhilst partitioning the result into a pair of lists, `List β × List γ`,\npartitioning the `.inl _` into the left list, and the `.inr _` into the right List.\n```\npartitionMap (id : Nat ⊕ Nat → Nat ⊕ Nat) [inl 0, inr 1, inl 2] = ([0, 2], [1])\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.partitionMap\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">partitionMap</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">γ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_3}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">β</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Sum\">⊕</a> <span class=\"fn\">γ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">γ</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/69a1d0485e241a494d69d3e2c98ad988f4396dcd/src/Init/Data/List/BasicAux.lean#L154-L160","name":"List.partitionM.go","line":154,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.partitionM.go","doc":"Auxiliary for `partitionM`:\n`partitionM.go p l acc₁ acc₂` returns `(acc₁.toList ++ left, acc₂.toList ++ right)`\nif `partitionM p l` returns `(left, right)`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.partitionM.go\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">partitionM</span>.<span class=\"name\">go</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Monad\">Monad</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> (<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/69a1d0485e241a494d69d3e2c98ad988f4396dcd/src/Init/Data/List/BasicAux.lean#L134-L160","name":"List.partitionM","line":134,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.partitionM","doc":"Monadic generalization of `List.partition`.\n\nThis uses `Array.toList` and which isn't imported by `Init.Data.List.Basic` or `Init.Data.List.Control`.\n```\ndef posOrNeg (x : Int) : Except String Bool :=\n  if x > 0 then pure true\n  else if x < 0 then pure false\n  else throw \"Zero is not positive or negative\"\n\npartitionM posOrNeg [-1, 2, 3] = Except.ok ([2, 3], [-1])\npartitionM posOrNeg [0, 2, 3] = Except.error \"Zero is not positive or negative\"\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.partitionM\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">partitionM</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Monad\">Monad</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> (<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/69a1d0485e241a494d69d3e2c98ad988f4396dcd/src/Init/Data/List/BasicAux.lean#L130-L130","name":"List.tail!_cons","line":130,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.tail!_cons","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.tail!_cons\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">tail!_cons</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">::</a> <span class=\"fn\">l</span>).<a href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.tail!\">tail!</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">l</span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/69a1d0485e241a494d69d3e2c98ad988f4396dcd/src/Init/Data/List/BasicAux.lean#L120-L128","name":"List.tail!","line":120,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.tail!","doc":"Drops the first element of the list.\n\nIf the list is empty, this function panics when executed, and returns the empty list.\nSee `tail` and `tailD` for safer alternatives.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.tail!\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">tail!</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/69a1d0485e241a494d69d3e2c98ad988f4396dcd/src/Init/Data/List/BasicAux.lean#L108-L116","name":"List.head!","line":108,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.head!","doc":"Returns the first element in the list.\n\nIf the list is empty, this function panics when executed, and returns `default`.\nSee `head` and `headD` for safer alternatives.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.head!\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">head!</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/69a1d0485e241a494d69d3e2c98ad988f4396dcd/src/Init/Data/List/BasicAux.lean#L94-L102","name":"List.getLast!","line":94,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.getLast!","doc":"Returns the last element in the list.\n\nIf the list is empty, this function panics when executed, and returns `default`.\nSee `getLast` and `getLastD` for safer alternatives.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.getLast!\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">getLast!</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/69a1d0485e241a494d69d3e2c98ad988f4396dcd/src/Init/Data/List/BasicAux.lean#L90-L90","name":"List.getD_nil","line":90,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.getD_nil","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.getD_nil\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">getD_nil</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α✝</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α✝</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">]</a>.<a href=\"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.getD\">getD</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span> <span class=\"fn\">d</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">d</span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/69a1d0485e241a494d69d3e2c98ad988f4396dcd/src/Init/Data/List/BasicAux.lean#L81-L88","name":"List.getD","line":81,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/BasicAux.html#List.getD","doc":"Returns the `i`-th element in the list (zero-based).\n\nIf the index is out of bounds (`i ≥ as.length`), this function returns `fallback`.\nSee also `get?` and `get!`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><spa